      <head altrender="biography" id="a2">BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE </head> 
      <p>Professor Emerita of Human Development and former Director of the
        Bronfenbrenner Life Course Center, Cornell University.</p> 
    </bioghist> 
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520"> 
      <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head> 
      <p>Includes course material, publications, correspondence, grant
        proposals, and videos pertaining to Moen's carrer in the Dept. of Human
        Development and as founding Director of the Bronfenbrenner Life Course Center
        in the College of Human Ecology.</p> 
    </scopecontent> 
